3eFrom the cache, follow the rock formation to the left down by a river of lava. At the end are some small ruins, the totem piece is inside.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4443968\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4443968\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The totem piece is inside the ruins at the end of the lava river.\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/1599/15997278/4443968-galawain13.jpeg 480w\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eThe totem piece is inside the ruins at the end of the lava river.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"Antler_of_the_Pursued_Stag\"\u003eAntler of the Pursued Stag\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cfigure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443970-galawain18.jpeg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4443970\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1599/15997278/4443970-galawain18.jpeg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4443970\"\u003e\u003c